Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: spamfighter
Version: 0.2.0
Summary: Web-service fighting spam and other unsolicited messages
Home-page: http://spam-fighter.ru/
Author: Andrey Smirnov
Author-email: me@smira.ru
License: GNU GPL
Download-URL: http://spam-fighter.ru/rus/Downloads
Description: SpamFighter combines several methods for filtering spam and other unsolicited messages (comments, chat etc.):
        - rule-based filtering
        - trained models
        - black-lists
        - frequency checking
        - and many more.
        
        SpamFighter provides XML- and JSON-RPC API for incoming message filtering and configuration requests. It comes with
        lightweight browser-based configuration tool, examples, plugin architecture and much more.
        
